  FROM jadwal_skripsi
  WHERE nama_mahasiswa LIKE '%Weldira Tarigan%'

),

    trim(substr(list_dosen, 1, instr(list_dosen, '|')-1)) AS dosen,
    substr(list_dosen, instr(list_dosen, '|')+1)           AS rest
  FROM seminar
  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    trim(substr(rest, 1, instr(rest, '|')-1)),
    substr(rest, instr(rest, '|')+1)
  FROM split
  WHERE rest <> ''
)

  SELECT daftar_dosen || '|' AS list_dosen
  FROM jadwal_skripsi
  WHERE tanggal = '2024-01-04'
    AND semester = 'Ganjil'
    AND pekan = 6

  SELECT
    trim(substr(list_dosen, 1, instr(list_dosen, '|')-1)) AS dosen,
    substr(list_dosen, instr(list_dosen, '|')+1)           AS rest
  FROM seminar
  UNION ALL
  SELECT
    trim(substr(rest, 1, instr(rest, '|')-1)),
    substr(rest, instr(rest, '|')+1)

)

FROM split
